Flattybird

Pole
1. Move the poles
2. Make the poles re-appear when it go out of the container
3. Change the poles speed before it re-appear
4. Change the poles height before it re-appear

Bird
1. Move the bird down
2. Move the bird up when space key is pressed

Score
1. Update score if bird successfully passes the poles

Game over
1. If bird hits pole_1
2. If bird hits pole_2
3. If bird hits the top of the container
4. If bird hits the bottom of the container

